<div class="wrapper about">
  <div class="inline-logo">
    <img src="<%= image_url('logo2.png') %>" />
  </div>
  <p>Do you know the thoughts of your users?</p>

  <p>Do you need a Contact Us form, but don't feel like writing the HTML and developing an API for just one form?</p>

  <p>Look no further than Promulgation.ninja! With the power of our magical ninja you can unlock your true potential and <em>Rule the Galaxy</em>!</p>
</div>

<form action="<%= session_url %>" method="POST" class="wrapper">
  <input
    type="hidden"
    name="authenticity_token"
    value="<%= form_authenticity_token %>"
  >

  <label>
    Name
    <input type="text"     name="user[name]"     autofocus />
  </label>

  <label>
    Password
    <input type="password" name="user[password]"           />
  </label>

  <input class="good-button" type="submit" value="Login" />
  <input class="good-button guest-button" type="submit" value="Login as Guest" />
</form>
